data.description: Mountain Views Galore !! INVESTORS NO RENTAL CAPS ! BUYER INCENTIVE 10K IN CLOSING COSTS OFFERED ,LOCATED just off I-575 welcome to your newer home in Worley Preserve community, located in the Jasper, Georgia. Nearly new construction, and is sure to impress with its fantastic floor plan . Modern design home with large spaces . As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by foyer with a large great room that has lots of natural light. The entry foyer has a bedroom and full bathroom for guests/ office area or flex room . The open floor plan flows seamlessly from the living room to the gourmet kitchen, making it ideal for entertaining guests. The kitchen is a true masterpiece, featuring new granite countertops that run throughout the entire kitchen., tile backsplash with upgrades under mount lighting. The kitchen has gas range with stainless steel appliances and custom cabinetry. The kitchen island provides ample space for meal prep and doubles as a breakfast bar for casual dining. Step outside the back patio that has incredible views of the N Georgia Mountains, perfect setting for outdoor entertaining. . . The upper level of the home features a primary bedroom suite which can also become a true seating area , office or flex area. Primary Bathroom with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and a large walk-in closet with custom closets systems . Three additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for guests or family. The laundry room located upstairs is large and can be used for storage items,.The home has been impeccably maintained and is move-in ready.
